---
/**
 * PaddleBlock — Mike's current pickleball paddle.
 *
 * Dedicated "the paddle" block. 11SIX24 Vapor Power 2 — his daily driver.
 * Rich product card: image, specs, price, link. Independent from the
 * pickleball-sport block so it reads as a gear recommendation, not news.
 *
 * AFFILIATE — TODO (when Mike is approved by 11SIX24):
 *   11SIX24 runs an ambassador program (https://11six24.com/pages/ambassador-program)
 *   paying $15 store credit OR $10 cash per paddle sold. Approved ambassadors
 *   get a referral link + shareable discount code. Once Mike applies + is
 *   approved, swap:
 *     - The `href=https://11six24.com/products/vapor-power-2` below for
 *       the tracked referral URL they provide.
 *     - Optionally surface the discount code as a small chip on the card
 *       (e.g. "POINTCAST · 5% off").
 *   Full findings in docs/11six24-affiliate.md.
 */
---

<section class="mt-10 mb-8" id="paddle">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
    <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-rule/40"></div>
    <h2 class="font-mono text-[0.58rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-ink-soft/60">
      The Paddle &middot; <span class="text-warm">mike’s daily</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-rule/40"></div>
  </div>

  <a
    href="https://11six24.com/products/vapor-power-2"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener"
    class="group relative block rounded-xl border-2 border-ink/80 bg-card overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
      <div class="relative md:w-1/2 bg-card overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Editorial paddle photo — generated via Nano Banana (see
             designs/paddle/). Stylized to match the warm-cream palette,
             golden-hour lighting, 3/4 diagonal composition. Not a reproduction
             of 11SIX24's product photography — an original editorial image. -->
        <img
          src="/images/vapor-power-2.jpg"
          alt="11SIX24 Vapor Power 2 paddle — editorial product shot on cream paper"
          class="block w-full aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-square object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1400"
          height="1050"
        />
        <!-- Midcentury corner dots overlay -->
        <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 w-3 h-3 bg-warm" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="absolute top-2 right-2 w-3 h-3 bg-ink" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="absolute bottom-2 left-2 w-3 h-3 bg-ink" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-3 h-3 bg-warm" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 md:p-6 md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center">
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.52rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-warm mb-1">
          recommend · $209
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-serif italic text-[1.4rem] text-ink leading-tight mb-3">
          The best value in pickleball.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[0.92rem] text-ink/75 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          Gen 4 full-foam floating core, carbon fiber face, HexGrit surface.
          2,335 RPM spin — 4th highest on record across 440+ paddles tested.
          98% grit retention after 100+ hours. $209 vs. $289+ for comparable
          builds elsewhere.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="p-2 rounded-sm border border-rule/30 bg-paper/60 text-center">
            <p class="font-mono text-[0.42rem] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-ink-soft/55">weight</p>
            <p class="font-mono text-[0.82rem] font-bold text-ink">8.0–8.3 oz</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-2 rounded-sm border border-rule/30 bg-paper/60 text-center">
            <p class="font-mono text-[0.42rem] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-ink-soft/55">core</p>
            <p class="font-mono text-[0.82rem] font-bold text-ink">16mm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-2 rounded-sm border border-rule/30 bg-paper/60 text-center">
            <p class="font-mono text-[0.42rem] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-ink-soft/55">UPA</p>
            <p class="font-mono text-[0.82rem] font-bold text-ink">approved</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.54rem] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-warm group-hover:underline">
          Get one ↗
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
</section>
